  "body": "### Component\n\nForge\n\n### Describe the feature you would like\n\nI know `forge build` can generate ABI files inside the `out` folder, \r\n\r\nbut they are quite large for Frontend to use them. Because those files have lots of other data within them.\r\n\r\nAnd they do not contain the latest deployment addresses.\r\n\r\nIs there a way for Foundry to generate such ABI and deployment address in json formats for each of selected contracts? \r\n\n\n### Additional context\n\n_No response_",
